title: Foreign Minister Bogdan Aurescu visits the Yad Vashem Memorial (Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Romania) ...
text: ( Source : Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Romania ) On the first day of his visit to the State of Israel , Romanian Foreign Minister Bogdan Aurescu visited the Yad Vashem Memorial , where he attended a ceremony of lighting the Eternal Flare .
